code: @Test public void testAhcComponentClientConfig() throws Exception {     super.testAhcComponentClientConfig().     Endpoint ahcEndpoint = context.getEndpoint(getAhcEndpointUri()).     assertTrue(ahcEndpoint instanceof AhcEndpoint).     assertEquals(1, ((AhcEndpoint) ahcEndpoint).getClientConfig().getMaxConnections()).     assertEquals(3, ((AhcEndpoint) ahcEndpoint).getClientConfig().getMaxRequestRetry()).     assertEquals(true, ((AhcEndpoint) ahcEndpoint).getClientConfig().isFollowRedirect()). }
